						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the shrine near the Gangamma temple.</p>						

						<p>It records the construction of a tank and digging of channels at Ponnavōlu by Kāmarusu Timmayya and also records the gift of 3 <hi rend="italic">khaṇḍigās</hi> of land to the gods Ishṭakāmēśvara and Bhairavēśvara.</p>						

						</summary>
